data.description: Open 1/21 from 2-4PM! This fully renovated gem in Columbus' Louis Heights offers a seamless blend of modern comfort and classic appeal. Enjoy the new LVP flooring and fresh paint, as well as the tastefully updated bathroom and kitchen adorned with stainless steel appliances. The spacious living room has a decorative fireplace, creating a cozy focal point. The two car detached garage and full basement provide ample storage space. Entertain in the fenced backyard, and enjoy off-street parking in the driveway! Being in close proximity of Italian Village, John Glenn Airport, and Easton Town Center, with convenient access to I-71, this property poses an amazing opportunity to invest or move into one of the top 3 markets in the country!
